Output spinners.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 32
Set Width 2400
Set Height 600
Set Framerate 30
Set Padding 20
Hide
Type "cargo build --example spinners 2>/dev/null"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Type "cargo run --example spinners 2>/dev/null"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show
Sleep 2s
Type "l"
Sleep 2s
Type "l"
Sleep 2s
Type "l"
Sleep 2s
Type "q"
